f(n) = 2^n \cdot g(n)
2^n \cdot g(n) = n + 2^n \cdot g(n-1)
g(n) - g(n-1) = n \cdot 2^{-n}
g(n) = g_0 + \sum_{k=0}^n k \cdot 2^{-k}
g_0 = \frac{1}{2}
